		<tu tuid="common-voice:web/locales/en/messages.ftl:stayintouch" srclang="en-US">
			<tuv xml:lang="en-US">
				<seg>We at Mozilla are building a community around voice technology. We would like to stay in touch with updates, new data sources and to hear more about how you're using this data.</seg>
			</tuv>
			<tuv xml:lang="nhe">
				<seg>Ipan Mozilla titekitinj ipan se comunidad tlen tlatoli tecnologia.Tinekiskian tikamatize yankhuik tlatoli, yankhuik tekitl huan ti matiz kenikatza ti tekitin huan mo datos.</seg>
			</tuv>
		</tu>
		<tu tuid="common-voice:web/locales/en/messages.ftl:yes-receive-emails" srclang="en-US">
			<tuv xml:lang="en-US">
				<seg>Yes, send me emails. I’d like to stay informed about the Common Voice Project.</seg>
			</tuv>
			<tuv xml:lang="nhe">
				<seg>kenaj, xinechtlatlanilij nopa emails, ni neki nimatiz ipan Common Voice Project.</seg>
